== 製作 ==
影片使用了[[3D|3D]]技術拍攝，[[電影攝影機|電影攝影機]]為[[Paradise_FX|Paradise FX]]系統<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/19683|title='Drive Angry' Shot in REAL 3-D, Lusier Explains Why Post-3-D is Garbage|publisher=Bloody-Disgusting|access-date=2012-02-09|archive-date=2016-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331130333/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/19683|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並由[[蓋瑞·滕尼克利夫|蓋瑞·滕尼克利夫]]（Gary Tunnicliffe）負責[[特效|特效]]之製作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://shocktillyoudrop.com/news/topnews.php?id=14312|title=Who's Handling the FX for Drive Angry ?|publisher=Shock Till You Drop|access-date=2010-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304023454/http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/topnews.php?id=14312|archive-date=2010-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。片中米爾頓所駕駛的三部車分別為1963年出產的[[別克未來|別克未來]]（Buick Riviera）、1969年出產的[[道奇戰馬|道奇戰馬]]（Dodge Charger）和1971年出產的[[雪佛蘭Chevelle|雪佛蘭Chevelle]] SS 454<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/36762/drive-angry-patrick-lussier-talks-benefits-shooting-3d-as-oppossed-3d-conversion|title=Drive Angry: Patrick Lussier Talks the Benefits of Shooting in 3D as Opposed to 3D Conversion|publisher=DreadCentral|access-date=2012-02-09|archive-date=2014-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140520044339/http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/36762/drive-angry-patrick-lussier-talks-benefits-shooting-3d-as-oppossed-3d-conversion|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
影片於2010年7月23日首次播映於[[聖地亞哥國際動漫節|聖地亞哥國際動漫節]]（San Diego Comic-Con International）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/38440/sd-comic-con-10-schedule-friday-723|title=SD Comic-Con '10 – Schedule for Friday (7/23)|publisher=DreadCentral|access-date=2012-02-09|archive-date=2013-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928095422/http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/38440/sd-comic-con-10-schedule-friday-723|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於2011年2月25日於[[美國|美國]]上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/NE2Ub274GzrQ54|title=Disney Sets Mars Needs Mom Release Date|publisher=MovieWeb|accessdate=2012-02-09|archive-date=2010-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101222211531/http://www.movieweb.com/news/NE2Ub274GzrQ54|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
